creator: Mohican North Star Gaming & Resort
descriptionHtml:
The North Star Mohican Casino Resort mobile app gets you instant access to exciting promotions, live entertainment schedules, special offers and more. For Star Club Members, the experience gets even better. Login to view point balances and access to exclusive offers and promotions.

GAMING
What if the next jackpot were yours? With the hottest slots, exciting bingo sessions, and tons of table games, you're sure to find a favorite! The gaming action is nonstop at North Star Mohican Casino Resort.

STAY
Cozy up in the Wisconsin Northwoods! Our luxury hotel boasts a contemporary architectural style with tall glass windows so you can admire the beauty of the surrounding landscape. After a night of non-stop excitement on the gaming floor, a delicious dining experience, or an indulgent spa treatment, settle in to one of our environmentally friendly guest rooms and get ready to rest easy.

DINING
Whether you prefer a sit-down experience or a grab-and-go meal, we’ve got what you’re craving, and it’s all made with the freshest ingredients. Our Aroma Deli & Café is a great place to grab a sandwich and get back to the games. Love live music and draft beer? Check out The Groove! For delicious American favorites, The Longhouse offers breakfast, lunch, and dinner.

AMENITIES
Looking to indulge? Let us pamper you at the Tarradea Salon & Spa. Want to spend time in the great outdoors? Visit the Pine Hills Golf Course for a round of golf. There are more ways to have fun at North Star Mohican Casino Resort! When you visit, we want you to have a blast, but also feel comfortable and relaxed with amenities that make you feel right at home.

DIRECTIONS
You can find us located off of Highway 29 on County Road A between the Villages of Gresham and Bowler in Shawano County, between Green Bay and Wausau. For directions, visit our Contact Page.

MORE POINTS, MORE REWARDS
Free Play, hotel discounts, concert tickets, and more — join the Star Club to get in on the perks! Signing up for the club is easy and free. Just visit the Star Club desk to get started. Once you have a Star Club card, start playing your favorite games and earning points. The first 10 points you earn gets you $10 in Free Play! PLUS, new members get 5X the points for the first 30 days!

The more points you earn, the more benefits you’ll receive! Points are redeemable for Free Play, gas, meals, golf packages, and more. See our Star Club Benefits chart below for a full list of rewards.

Your membership status is based on a 6-month earning period: January 1 – June 30 and July 1 – December 31.

LOCATION SERVICES
Get rewarded during your next visit! When you enable Location Services for the North Star Mohican app, you qualify for exclusive, limited-time offers that you don’t want to miss!
descriptionShort: Download the North Star Mohican Resort Casino mobile app now!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
General bug fixes and performance improvements.
We are always working on updates to improve your app experience.
